code: @Override public void process(Exchange exchange) throws Exception {     MqttClient client = getEndpoint().getClient().     String topic = exchange.getIn().getHeader(PahoConstants.CAMEL_PAHO_OVERRIDE_TOPIC, getEndpoint().getTopic(), String.class).     int qos = exchange.getIn().getHeader(PahoConstants.CAMEL_PAHO_MSG_QOS, getEndpoint().getQos(), Integer.class).     boolean retained = exchange.getIn().getHeader(PahoConstants.CAMEL_PAHO_MSG_RETAINED, getEndpoint().isRetained(), Boolean.class).     byte[] payload = exchange.getIn().getBody(byte[].class).     MqttMessage message = new MqttMessage(payload).     message.setQos(qos).     message.setRetained(retained).     log.debug("Publishing to topic: {}, qos: {}, retrained: {}", topic, qos, retained).     client.publish(topic, message). }
